snippet.title: Best VGM 1292 - Radiant Historia - The Garden Where the Celestite Lies
snippet.description:

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo DS
Radiant Historia (2011)
The Garden Where the Celestite Lies
Yoko Shimomura
